            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a high heat, and once hot, add the <strong>steaks</strong> and cook for an initial 3-4 min on each side or until browned</p><p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>remaining ground smoked paprika</strong> with your <strong>tomato ketchup</strong>, your<strong> wholegrain mustard</strong>, <strong>honey</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> and 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[60ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[80ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> – this is your <strong>barbecue sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1644924625918-x200.jpg",
