            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the steaks are resting, add the <strong>chopped lettuce </strong>and<strong> sliced cucumber </strong>to the bowl with the <strong>quick-pickled shallots</strong></p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and toss together – this is your <strong>pickled salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
