            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> rested</strong> <strong>BBQ</strong> <strong>pork steaks</strong> with the <strong>smoky</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> and <strong>pickled salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle any <strong>remaining BBQ sauce</strong> over the potatoes</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
